# spartan-forge repository mappings
# Format: <agent-group>  <path-to-repo>
# Use "generic" for the generic FDE team, or a project name for project-specific agents.
# Paths support ~ for home directory.
#
# Copy this file to .repos.conf and fill in your local paths.
# .repos.conf is gitignored — never commit it.

# Examples:
# generic              ~/projects/my-side-project
# my-client-project    ~/work/client/their-repo
# finding-memo         ~/PycharmProjects/finding-memo
